	<article class="post-171454 post type-post status-publish hentry category-todays-economist tag-capital-gains-tax tag-decisions-and-verdicts tag-income-tax tag-internal-revenue-service tag-supreme-court-us des-capital-gains-tax des-decisions-and-verdicts des-income-tax org-internal-revenue-service org-supreme-court-us" id="post-171454">
